<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV108">
<l>kēṭilcīrva rattaṉāykke ṭumvaratta yaṉara</l>
<l>ṉāṭiṉōṭu nāṭṭamāyi rattaṉāṭu naṇṇiṉum</l>
<l>vīṭatāṉa pōkameyti vīṟṟirunta pōtiluṅ</l>
<l>kūṭumācai yallatoṉṟu koḷvaṉōku ṟippilē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if the lands—of Aja-Brahmā with excellent, evil-free boons,</l>
<l>Hara-Śiva whose boon is [to cause] destruction,</l>
<l>along with the land of the thousand-eyed [Indra]—approach [me],</l>
<l>Even when [I] sit in state having obtained the enjoyment that is liberation,</l>
<l>Would I have in [my] inmost thought anything other than the desire to unite with [You]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
